        <updateDate>2010-05-11T16:20:56Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p> Mortgage Servicing Conflict Elimination Act of 2010 - Amends the Truth in Lending Act to prohibit the servicer of a residential mortgage loan (or an affiliate) from owning or holding any interest in any other residential mortgage loan secured by the same dwelling or residential real property. <br> </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
